@startuml
title Feature 028 admin referral sequence

actor "Маркетинг-администратор" as MarketingAdmin
actor "CRM-администратор" as CrmAdmin
actor "Партнер-спонсор" as Sponsor
actor "Кандидат" as Candidate
participant "Frontend web-shell\n/admin/referrals" as Frontend
participant "Auth/RBAC module" as Auth
participant "admin-referral API" as AdminReferral
database "admin_ref_* tables" as AdminReferralDb
participant "partner-onboarding API\nfeature #008" as Onboarding
participant "platform analytics layer\nfeature #025" as Analytics

MarketingAdmin -> Frontend: открыть раздел лендингов и инвайтов
Frontend -> Auth: получить session context и permission scopes
Auth --> Frontend: roles, scopes, locale, message dictionaries
Frontend -> AdminReferral: GET /api/admin-referral/landing-variants
AdminReferral -> Auth: проверить ADMIN_REFERRAL_VIEW
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: найти landing variants
AdminReferral --> Frontend: список лендингов

MarketingAdmin -> Frontend: создать business landing draft
Frontend -> AdminReferral: POST /landing-variants
AdminReferral -> Auth: проверить ADMIN_REFERRAL_MANAGE
AdminReferral -> AdminReferral: validate slug, blocks, active window
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: сохранить landing, version, blocks, audit
AdminReferral --> Frontend: AdminReferralLandingDetailResponse

MarketingAdmin -> Frontend: открыть preview и активировать
Frontend -> AdminReferral: POST /landing-variants/{landingId}/preview
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: собрать draft render model
AdminReferral --> Frontend: preview render model
Frontend -> AdminReferral: POST /landing-variants/{landingId}/activate
AdminReferral -> AdminReferral: validate required blocks and conflicts
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: active version, audit event
AdminReferral --> Frontend: messageCode STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_REFERRAL_LANDING_SAVED

CrmAdmin -> Frontend: настроить registration funnel
Frontend -> AdminReferral: POST /funnels
AdminReferral -> Auth: проверить ADMIN_REFERRAL_FUNNEL_MANAGE
AdminReferral -> AdminReferral: validate steps and consent codes
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: сохранить funnel version and audit
AdminReferral --> Frontend: funnel detail
Frontend -> AdminReferral: POST /funnels/{funnelId}/activate
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: active funnel version
AdminReferral --> Frontend: messageCode STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_REFERRAL_FUNNEL_SAVED

CrmAdmin -> Frontend: сгенерировать referral code
Frontend -> AdminReferral: POST /referral-codes + Idempotency-Key
AdminReferral -> Auth: проверить ADMIN_REFERRAL_CODE_MANAGE
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: найти по idempotency key
alt код уже создан
  AdminReferralDb --> AdminReferral: existing referral code
else новый idempotency key
  AdminReferral -> AdminReferral: validate code active window and owner
  AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: insert referral code and audit event
end
AdminReferral --> Frontend: referral code response

CrmAdmin -> Frontend: задать attribution policy
Frontend -> AdminReferral: PUT /attribution-policy
AdminReferral -> Auth: проверить ADMIN_REFERRAL_ATTRIBUTION_MANAGE
AdminReferral -> AdminReferral: validate priority sources
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: save policy and audit
AdminReferral --> Frontend: attribution policy response

Sponsor -> Frontend: открыть sponsor cabinet
Frontend -> AdminReferral: получить active referral rules для partner link
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: active landing, funnel, referral code
AdminReferral --> Frontend: referral link context
Frontend --> Sponsor: personal referral link

Candidate -> Frontend: открыть referral link
Frontend -> AdminReferral: track LANDING_VIEWED and validate referral context
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: conversion event
Frontend -> Onboarding: start registration with campaign/referral context
Onboarding -> AdminReferral: validate referral code and resolve attribution
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: attribution event, conversion event
AdminReferral --> Onboarding: selected sponsor attribution
Onboarding --> Frontend: registration state
Frontend -> Analytics: consent-aware conversion events

CrmAdmin -> Frontend: исправить спорную attribution
Frontend -> AdminReferral: POST /attribution/override
AdminReferral -> Auth: проверить ADMIN_REFERRAL_ATTRIBUTION_OVERRIDE
AdminReferral -> AdminReferral: validate reason code and comment
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: attribution override, conversion event, audit
AdminReferral --> Frontend: STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_REFERRAL_ATTRIBUTION_OVERRIDDEN

MarketingAdmin -> Frontend: открыть conversion report
Frontend -> AdminReferral: GET /analytics/conversions
AdminReferral -> Auth: проверить ADMIN_REFERRAL_ANALYTICS_VIEW
AdminReferral -> AdminReferralDb: aggregate conversion metrics
AdminReferral --> Frontend: totals and rows without secrets

@enduml
